oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Chapman Alexander & Co
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Edwin Best
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Greenback (Tenn.); Chapman Alexander & Co.; Business;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Group of men posing outside the Chapman Alexander & Co building. Hand notation on top says building is about 15 feet wide. Frame building. Board and batten siding with clipboards on the gable ends. Wood shingles. Windows and door in front. Porch on side. Names written in cursive on bottom and side of picture.
